<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 2889/93 of 21 October 1993 laying down certain detailed rules for the application of Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 as regards the supplements to the special premium for producers of beef and veal and to the premium for maintaining suckler cows </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 2889/93, millega kehtestatakse veise- ja vasikalihatootjatele makstavat t&auml;iendavat erilisatasu ja ammlehmade pidamise eest makstavat t&auml;iendavat lisatasu k&auml;sitleva m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 teatavad &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad 21. oktoober 1993 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 of 19 July 1993 introducing specific measures in respect of certain agricultural products for the benefit of the smaller Aegean Islands (1), and in particular Article 6 (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 19. juuli 1993. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 v&auml;iksemate Egeuse mere saarte heaks teatavate p&otilde;llumajandustoodete suhtes kehtestatavate erimeetmete kohta, (1) eriti selle artikli 6 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 3813/92 of 28 December 1992 on the unit of account and the conversion rates to be applied for the purposes of the common agricultural policy (2), and in particular Article 6 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 28. detsembri 1992. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 3813/92 &uuml;hises p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitikas rakendatavate arvestus&uuml;hiku ja &uuml;mberarvestuskursside kohta, (2) eriti selle artiklit 6, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 provides for specific measures to assist livestock production in the smaller Aegean Islands; whereas such measures involve, in the beef and veal sector, a supplement to the special premium for male bovine animals and to the premium for maintaining suckler cows as provided for respectively in Articles 4b and 4d of Council Regulation (EEC) No 805/68 of 27 June 1968 on the common organization of the market in beef and veal (3), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 125/93 (4); whereas provision should be made for those supplements to be granted under the rules applicable to those premium schemes; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 s&auml;testatakse erimeetmed loomakasvatustoodangu edendamiseks v&auml;iksematel Egeuse mere saartel; veise- ja vasikalihasektoris h&otilde;lmavad k&otilde;nealused meetmed pullide puhul makstavat t&auml;iendavat erilisatasu ja ammlehmade pidamise eest makstavat t&auml;iendavat lisatasu, mis on vastavalt ette n&auml;htud n&otilde;ukogu 27. juuni 1986. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 805/68 (veise- ja vasikalihaturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (3) viimati muudetud komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 125/93 (4)) artiklitega 4b ja 4d; tuleks s&auml;testada nende t&auml;iendavate lisatasude andmine k&otilde;nealuste lisatasukavade rakenduseeskirjade alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3886/92 (5), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1909/93 (6), specifies 1 January as the date of application of the agricultural conversion rate; whereas the specific measures entered into force on 1 August 1993; whereas it is therefore appropriate that the latter be the date used, for 1993, for the conversion of such aid into national currency; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3886/92, (5) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1909/93, (6) s&auml;testatakse, et p&otilde;llumajandusliku &uuml;mberarvestuskursi rakendusjuht on 1. jaanuar; erimeetmed j&otilde;ustusid 1. augustil 1993; seet&otilde;ttu on asjakohane, et viimati nimetatud kuup&auml;ev on 1993. aasta puhul k&otilde;nealuse abi omav&auml;&auml;ringusse &uuml;mberarvestamise p&auml;ev; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas certain producers had, by the date from which this Regulation applies, already submitted applications; whereas the submission of a new application for the supplement could complicate the administration of these measures; whereas, therefore, the supplement should also be paid against those applications; </inglise>
<eesti> teatavad tootjad on k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse kohaldamise kuup&auml;evaks juba esitanud taotlusi; t&auml;iendava abi jaoks uue taotluse esitamine v&otilde;ib raskendada k&otilde;nealuste meetmete haldamist; seep&auml;rast tuleks ka t&auml;iendavat abi anda esitatud taotluste p&otilde;hjal; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to achieve the objectives set for the territories in question by Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 and to take account of their specific needs, the competent authorities should be permitted to adopt additional provisions with regard to the granting of such aid; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 k&otilde;nealuste territooriumide jaoks seatud eesm&auml;rkide saavutamiseks ja nende erivajaduste arvessev&otilde;tmiseks peaks p&auml;devatel asutustel olema lubatud v&otilde;tta k&otilde;nealuse abi andmiseks vastu t&auml;iendavaid s&auml;tteid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas provision should be made for the detailed rules to apply as from the entry into force of the scheme adopted for the smaller Aegean islands, that is, from 1 August 1993; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks ette n&auml;ha &uuml;ksikasjalike eeskirjade kohaldamine v&auml;iksemate Egeuse mere saarte kohta alates vastuv&otilde;etud kava j&otilde;ustumisest, s.o 1. augustist 1993; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Beef and Veal, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las veise- ja vasikalihaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The supplement to the special premium for the fattening of male bovine animals, provided for in the first indent of Article 6 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 in respect of the smaller Aegean islands, shall be granted on the basis of the rules applicable to applications under the scheme for the special premium for beef and veal producers. </inglise>
<eesti> V&auml;iksemate Egeuse mere saarte puhul antakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 artikli 6 l&otilde;ike 1 esimese taandega etten&auml;htud isasveiste nuumamise t&auml;iendavat erilisatasu eeskirjade p&otilde;hjal, mida kohaldatakse veise- ja vasikalihatootjatele antava erilisatasu kava raames esitatavate taotluste suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The supplement to the premium for maintaining suckler cows, provided for in the second indent of Article 6 (1) of Regulation (EEC) No 2019/93 in respect of beef and veal producers in the smaller Aegean islands, shall be granted on the basis of the rules applicable to applications under the scheme for the premium for maintaining suckler cows. </inglise>
<eesti> V&auml;iksemate Egeuse mere saarte puhul antakse m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2019/93 artikli 6 l&otilde;ike 1 teise taandega etten&auml;htud ammlehmade pidamise eest makstava t&auml;iendavat lisatasu eeskirjade p&otilde;hjal, mida kohaldatakse ammlehmade eest makstava lisatasu kava raames esitatavate taotluste suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For 1993 and notwithstanding Article 53 of Regulation (EEC) No 3886/92, the conversion into national currency of the amount of the supplement provided for in Articles 1 and 2 shall be made by applying the agricultural conversion rate in force on 1 August 1993. </inglise>
<eesti> Olenemata m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3886/92 artiklist 53 kohaldatakse artiklites 1 ja 2 etten&auml;htud t&auml;iendava lisatasu summade omav&auml;&auml;ringusse &uuml;mberarvestamisel 1. augustil 1993. aastal kehtivat p&otilde;llumajanduslikku &uuml;mberarvestuskurssi. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The aid provided for in Articles 1 and 2 shall also be paid to producers who, on the date of application of this Regulation, have already submitted applications for the special premium and/or the premium for maintaining suckler cows in respect of 1993 and who fulfil the conditions of eligibility laid down for those premiums. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklites 1 ja 2 etten&auml;htud abi antakse tootjatele, kes on esitanud k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumiskuup&auml;evaks erilisatasu ja/v&otilde;i ammlehmade eest makstava lisatasu taotlused aastaks 1993 ja kes vastavad k&otilde;nealuste lisatasude saamise tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The Greek authorities may adopt, as necessary, additional provisions with regard to the granting of the supplements referred to in Articles 1 and 2. </inglise>
<eesti> Kreeka ametiasutused v&otilde;ivad vastavalt vajadusele v&otilde;tta vastu t&auml;iendavaid s&auml;tteid artiklites 1 ja 2 osutatud t&auml;iendavate lisatasude andmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise> They shall inform the Commission of such action forthwith. </inglise>
<eesti> Nad teatavad sellisest s&auml;tetest viivitamata komisjonile. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The Greek authorities shall notify the Commission each year, by 31 March at the latest, of the number of animals in respect of which the supplements have been applied for and granted. </inglise>
<eesti> Kreeka ametiasutused teatavad komisjonile igal aastal hiljemalt 31. m&auml;rtsiks loomade arvu, kelle puhul t&auml;iendavaid lisatasusid on taotletud ja antud. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamise p&auml;eval. </eesti>
<inglise> It shall apply with effect from 1 August 1993. </inglise>
<eesti> Seda kohaldatakse alates 1. augustist 1993. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 21 October 1993. </inglise>
